Package: brakeza3d
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Open-source 3D game engine with built-in editor and Lua scripting
 Brakeza3D is a free and open-source 3D game engine designed for rapid game
 development. Features include a built-in visual editor (ImGui), Lua scripting,
 OpenGL deferred rendering pipeline, Bullet Physics integration, 3D model
 loading with skeletal animation (Assimp), and a node-based GLSL shader editor.
